text:
It is problematic for at least two reasons:

* it has quite a few chances to be a directory in use by the base operating system;
* if tomcat is built as root (which shouldn't happen but still), there may be the possibility to alter the contents of this directory.

Suggestions:

* change it to /var/tmp/tomcat-build, or the like;
* or don't define it at all in build.properties.default and raise an error at build time if user hasn't defined it in its own build.properties.
